msgid "Multimedia Player"
msgstr "Multimedieafspiller"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kaffeine.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Kaffeine is a media player. What makes it different from the others is its "
"excellent support of digital TV (DVB). Kaffeine has user-friendly interface, "
"so that even first time users can start immediately playing their movies: "
"from DVD (including DVD menus, titles, chapters, etc.), VCD, or a file."
msgstr ""
"Kaffeine er en medieafspiller. Det der gør den anderledes end andre "
"afspillere er dens glimrende understøttelse af digitalt tv (DVB). Kaffeine "
"har en nem brugerflade, så selv helt nye brugere straks kan begynde at "
"afspille deres film fra dvd (inklusiv dvd-menuer, titler, kapitler osv.), "
"VCD eller en fil."

